Cc: pawel.moll@arm.com
Cc: robh+dt@kernel.org
Cc: tthayer.linux@gmail.com
Link: http://lkml.kernel.org/r/1433428128-7292-5-git-send-email-tthayer@opensource.altera.com
Signed-off-by: Borislav Petkov <bp@suse.de>
